results.title: Avengers (1963) #390
results.description: The Avengers attempt to unwind with a summer BBQ, but inevitably, things go awry. Hercules arrives on the scene with a young fortune-teller claiming to be the future son of Crystal and Quicksilver. Meanwhile, Wasp receives shocking news about her bank statement.

results.title: Avengers (1963) #391
results.description: After filing for bankruptcy, Wasp discovers that Tony Stark may be behind her financial ruin. Vision makes a horrifying discovery involving two residents of Avengers Mansion. Giant-Man collects all evidence and concludes that Kang has returned!

results.title: Avengers (1963) #392
results.description: Iron Man orders lockdown on Avengers Mansion to prevent any tampering of evidence. Space phantoms Malachi and Tobias, along with an imposter Luna, set a deviant plan into action. Will the Swordsman and Vision be able to stop the trio from capturing the Cotati?

results.title: The Past Is With Us Always
Avengers (1963) #393
results.description: Overpowered in a war of the future, Kang makes a desperate bid to return to the present. Wasp is left bloodied and beaten following a battle with an imposter Iron Man. Giant-Man makes every attempt to save her life, but will his efforts be enough?

results.title: Avengers (1963) #394
results.description: The Wasp emerges from her cocoon in an insect-like form. After being kidnapped by “big brother” Tuc, Luna makes a daring escape while rescuing Moonraker from Kang. Quicksilver faces a devastating blow when Luna’s rescue mission goes awry. Will this be the death of an Avenger?

results.title: Avengers (1963) #395
results.description: Kang sets his final plans into motion as a teenaged Tony Stark lies dying. Will the Avengers be able to save their fallen comrade? And will Kang ever restore the Avengers’ timeline?

results.title: Avengers (1963) #400
results.description: Loki has conjured the greatest enemies the Avengers have ever faced! Will Earth’s Mightiest Heroes be able to withstand the foes no single hero could?

items.name: X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Vol. 1 TPB (2007)

results.title: Avengers (1963) #401
results.description: The Avengers team-up with the X-Men to take down Onslaught. The teams track down Magneto, believing he is at fault. The team discovers that Magneto is now “Joseph”, a de-aged and amnesiac version of the X-Men’s foe. But why is Rogue fighting the Avengers tooth and nail to protect Joseph? And is this “de-aged Magneto” really the man he claims to be?

results.description: In the aftermath of Onslaught, the Avengers must commit to damage control. While trying to contain the wide spread damage, the team is attacked by the two mutants Post and Holocaust.
